= SDL_AddEventWatch =
Use this function to add a function which is called when an event is added to the queue.


== Syntax ==
```c++
void SDL_AddEventWatch(SDL_EventFilter filter,
                       void*           userdata)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''filter'''
|a function that gets called when an event happens; see [[#Remarks|Remarks]] for details
|-
|'''userdata'''
|^a pointer to the event queue to watch^
|}

